Release Notes

This page contains the release notes for the currently active versions of Google's DoubleClick for Publisher API. Release notes from some previous versions that are no longer available are exposed only for completeness.

  • Latest version: v201802
  • Previous versions: v201711, v201708, v201705

v201802

What's New

Line Items
  • Removed creativePersistenceType from Line Items, impacting LineItemService and ForecastService.
  • Added a lineItemType for Preferred Deals, which allows offering inventory to specific buyers.
Reports
  • For Ad Exchange Historical reports, the currency type can now be specified with adxReportCurrency.
  • Sales Manager and Ad Exchange Historical reports can now specify a time zone with timeZoneType.
  • Added DEMAND_CHANNEL_NAME and DEMAND_CHANNEL_ID dimensions.
  • Added REQUEST_TYPE dimension to distinguish how an ad was requested.
  • Added PROPOSAL_LINE_ITEM_TYPE dimension attribute in order to filter proposal line items.
  • Deprecated mediation dimensions (MEDIATION_GROUP_ID, MEDIATION_GROUP_NAME, MEDIATION_NETWORK, MEDIATION_NETWORK_TAG) in favor of new yield group dimensions (YIELD_GROUP_ID, YIELD_GROUP_NAME, YIELD_PARTNER, YIELD_PARTNER_TAG).
PQL
  • Added PpidSize column to Audience_Segment PQL table for determining the number of unique viewers in a segment.
  • Added EnabledForPreferredDeals and EnabledForProgrammaticGuaranteed columns to Programmatic_Buyer PQL table for determining which types a deals a buyer has enabled.
Creatives
  • Removed VpaidLinearCreative and VpaidLinearRedirectCreative as part of the Flash creative deprecation.

v201711

What's New

Please note that Ad Exchange historical reports will be run in the Pacific timezone in v201711. This will allow you to report on Bid and Deals metrics. If you need to continue running Ad Exchange historical reports in your network timezone, please stay on v201708. Future versions will support both options.

Creatives
  • Added getPreviewUrlsForNativeStyles to support generating in-site preview URLs for Native styles.
Ad Units
  • Added support for fluid sizes with isFluid field.
Video
  • Added CdnConfigurationService to support managing CDN configurations. A CdnConfiguration encapsulates information about where and how to ingest and deliver content enabled for DAI (Dynamic Ad Insertion).
  • Added startDateTimeType to LiveStreamEvents to support creating events that start immediately.
  • Added support for HLS settings in LiveStreamEvents.
Reporting
  • Added new Partner Management dimensions and metrics.

v201708

What's New

Creatives
  • Added support for setting skippableAdType on video creatives.
  • CreativeWrapperHtmlSnippet has been removed.
  • The header and footer fields on CreativeWrapper have been replaced by htmlHeader and htmlFooter strings.
  • Added support for setting VAST 4.0 mezzanine files on VideoRedirectCreatives
Sales Management
  • Removed the SyncProposalsWithMarketplace action. Proposals are now automatically synced with marketplace. This action is now a no-op in previous API versions.
  • Added support for Sales Management entities in the Change_History PQL table.
Reporting
  • Added new LAST_3_MONTHS as a DateRangeType to support the new UI option.
  • Removed deprecated partner metrics in favor of PARTNER_MANAGEMENT fields.

v201705

What's New

Inventory
  • The AdUnit.mobilePlatform field has been removed to align with UI features.
  • AdUnitAction fields RemoveAdUnitsFromPlacement and AssignAdUnitsToPlacement have been removed. Updates should happen through the Placement service.
  • AdUnit.inheritedAdSenseSettings has been removed. It has been replaced with AdUnit.adSenseSettings and AdUnit.adSenseSettingsSource to more easily support determining whether an AdUnit's adSenseSettings are inherited or directly specified.
Placements
  • Placement fields adSenseTargetingLocale, isAdsenseTargetingEnabled, targetingDescription, targetingSiteName, and targetingAdLocation have been removed to align with UI features.
Native Styles
  • Added NativeStyle.status field to expose the active/archived status of native styles.
Teams
  • Added performTeamAction method with ActivateTeams and DeativateTeams actions.
  • Added Team.status field to expose the active/inactive status of teams.
Roles
  • Added Role.status field to expose the active/inactive status of roles.
Creatives
  • Added support for creating ImageOverlayCreative.
Partner Management
  • Removed Company.Type enumerations for AFFILIATE_DISTRIBUTION_PARTNER, CONTENT_PARTNER.
  • Added Company.Type enumeration for PARTNER
  • Removed CrossSellingDistributor.
  • The AdUnit fields partnerId, isSharedByDistributor, and crossSellingDistributor have been removed.
Reporting
  • Major changes to DFP support for AdX reporting, v201705 brings complete feature parity to the AdX API.
  • Removed references to VAST version in error metrics, the new convention is VIDEO_ERRORS_VAST_ERROR_[CODE]_COUNT.
  • Added Active View average viewable time metrics.
  • Changed reporting of local sales metrics in CSV_DUMP format to micros with ISO code making automated parsing easier. For example: USD 3900000 is $3.9 (USD).
